### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000

### Register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Me (paste your token from login response below)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here



### Create Room (paste your login token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/rooms/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

{
  "name": "My First Room",
  "language": "javascript"
}

### Get My Rooms
GET http://localhost:5000/api/rooms/my-rooms
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

### Join Room (paste a roomId from create response)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/rooms/join/paste_room_id_here
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

### Get Single Room
GET http://localhost:5000/api/rooms/paste_room_id_here
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

### Save Snapshot
POST http://localhost:5000/api/rooms/paste_room_id_here/snapshot
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

{
  "code": "console.log('Hello CodeCollab!')"
}

### Run JavaScript Code
POST http://localhost:5000/api/execute/run
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

{
  "code": "console.log('Hello from CodeCollab!')",
  "language": "javascript"
}

### Run Python Code
POST http://localhost:5000/api/execute/run
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

{
  "code": "print('Hello from Python!')",
  "language": "python"
}

### Run Code with Error (to test stderr)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/execute/run
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer paste_your_token_here

{
  "code": "console.log(undefinedVariable)",
  "language": "javascript"
}